data.description: Gorgeous luxury ranch-3 bedroom/2 full bathroom/3 car garge in desirable Pine Hill area!Vaulted open concept kitchen/dining area/living room with a split bedroom floorplan.Lots of of upgrades throughout to make for a very modern design with vinyl plank flooring & mixture of white/stain cabinets.Kitchen has large island to entertain,pantry& dining area.Living room is very spacious with a gas fireplace.Primary bedroom is large with walkin closet& bathroom that includes double sinks,heated towel bar,&shower with bulit in blue tooth speakers.2 additional bedrooms on the other side of the home with a large full bath in between.Downstairs has a room built & much more to finish with egress window.Large patio/stone edging with gazebo,hot tub & privacy treeline/yard.
